main event: A sighting of unidentified flying objects in San Rafael, California on August 9, 1965, reported various objects moving silently in the sky.
interesting points: The objects were described as dome-shaped and initially appeared singly before flying in formation., The sighting was observed between 1900 and 2100 local time., The objects hovered motionless at first before suddenly accelerating away., The observer used binoculars to view the objects., There were no confirmed reports from others at the same time, indicating poor quality of information overall.
witness description: The single observer was a male aged between 15-19, identified as a UFO watcher.
